Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.71,0:00:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,So I heard about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.17,0:00:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems like it was really rough.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.23,0:00:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you feel like a weight got \Nlifted off of your shoulders?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.74,0:00:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? From what?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.74,0:00:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you mean my sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.58,0:00:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,No, not that.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.71,0:00:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure that was rough, too, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.46,0:00:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah. Will you tell your sister congrats\Non finishing her exams for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.71,0:00:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,No, why would I?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.04,0:00:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do I have to give her a message from you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.47,0:00:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Though I'm happy to hear \Nyou say that. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.08,0:00:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Unbelievable, I never thought \NI'd get thanked like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.35,0:00:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I wasn't referring to your \Nlittle sister, though…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.52,0:00:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I meant that other little sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.29,0:00:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,There's something I want \Nto talk to you about.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.13,0:00:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.67,0:01:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,First of all, would you like to come in?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.33,0:02:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to drink more?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.54,0:02:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course. There are some \Ndays I just want to drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.92,0:02:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, alcohol helps make life\Ngo down a bit smoother.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.10,0:02:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it's more often the \Nroot cause of problems, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.33,0:03:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, I'll listen \Nto what you have to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.92,0:03:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. You won't listen to \Nme even when you're sober.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.92,0:03:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,This is true! Now then…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.58,0:03:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you wanna say?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.71,0:03:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to talk about us,\Nand what will happen with us in the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.96,0:03:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.85,0:03:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to let me in on all that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.71,0:03:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.00,0:03:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,This is about you and me. And also about Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.79,0:03:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, that's what you meant.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.50,0:03:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,This doesn't sound like \Nsomething I want to hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.75,0:03:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.96,0:03:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I still want you to listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.38,0:03:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I'm going home.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.88,0:03:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,There, I will talk to Mom about \Nmy future and what I want.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.29,0:04:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if I can't get what I want,\NI don't want to have any regrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.50,0:04:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to... at least make myself clear,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.71,0:04:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,so that I can accept the outcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.88,0:04:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. So I guess that's your answer, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.83,0:04:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's fine. You've \Ngrown a little, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.54,0:04:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I know what you want to say.\NIf you're serious about it, then I'll work with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.34,0:04:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll work with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.49,0:04:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.50,0:04:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom's not the type of person\Nto change course very easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.56,0:04:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'll put in a good word \Nfor you when appropriate.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.38,0:04:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That being said, I don't know\Nif that will be effective or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.25,0:04:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,However, you should go there with the assumption\Nthat you won't be back here for awhile.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.23,0:05:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I figured.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.25,0:05:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.08,0:05:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I was only allowed to come here\Nbecause she was worried about Yukino.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.58,0:05:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,If Yukino goes home,\Nshe probably won't be set free again so easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.49,0:05:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,First, pack up your things.\NThen you'll need to get in touch with Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.44,0:05:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes… I'll do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.60,0:05:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.75,0:05:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'll have free use of this \Nplace for awhile. That okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.33,0:05:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You can do what you want with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.88,0:05:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.29,0:05:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll help you pack up, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.17,0:05:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I can't let you do that for me, too…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.64,0:05:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's totally okay! I actually want you to let me help.\NI really like organizing things!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.88,0:05:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,But…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.46,0:05:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I think this is the only thing \NI'm able to help you with…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.92,0:05:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Let her do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.71,0:05:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Free labor is hard to find nowadays.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.50,0:05:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,That sounds good.\NWhy don't you go ahead and stay the night?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.88,0:06:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Would that be… asking too much?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.75,0:06:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'd love to!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.63,0:06:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.83,0:06:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's do some decluttering! I recently bought\Na ton of books on how to declutter!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.96,0:06:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Those books are the first thing\Nthat should be decluttered.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.92,0:06:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to the convenience store.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.04,0:06:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you need anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.21,0:06:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you went to the convenience store.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.08,0:06:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,This sort of thing feels a bit \Nlike a rendezvous, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.96,0:06:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't this more like an ambush?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.54,0:06:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's freezing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.46,0:06:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.58,0:06:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, cigarette smoke, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.42,0:06:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.45,0:06:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You were drinking for quite some time, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.82,0:06:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep, they wouldn't let me go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.77,0:06:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I almost got pulled into \Ngoing at it all night.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.45,0:06:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,O-oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.79,0:07:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm so glad I came home early.\NI was able to listen to what Yukino had to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.82,0:07:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.80,0:07:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Er, that's just kind of surprising.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.83,0:07:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What is?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.01,0:07:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,That you actually listened to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.34,0:07:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.00,0:07:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm still her older sister, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.02,0:07:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,If that's what Yukino has chosen, then I will support\Nthat decision, whether it's the right one or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.08,0:07:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,If she's making the wrong \Nchoice, shouldn't you stop her?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.92,0:07:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,She wouldn't listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.67,0:07:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,More importantly, I don't care either way.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.88,0:07:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Because nothing will change.\NWhether it works out or she gives up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.04,0:07:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody becomes an adult by giving up\Non various things like that, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.29,0:07:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I see…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.38,0:07:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have that sort of experience?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.24,0:07:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm, I wonder!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.98,0:07:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't matter here. We're \Ntalking about Yukino right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.25,0:07:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I think this is the first time \Nshe's ever made herself clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.75,0:07:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Please watch over her too, Hikigaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.50,0:08:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.79,0:08:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I acted like a big sister again…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.17,0:08:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you try being \Nlike that all the time?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.50,0:08:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,No way. I'm not like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.80,0:08:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You're always acting like a big brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.42,0:08:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, yeah… I am a big brother after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.29,0:08:18.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.25,0:08:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It must be nice to have an older brother like you.\NI wish I had one of those!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.89,0:08:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey…You're being an \Nannoying drunk right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.00,0:08:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no, I'm not drunk!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.04,0:08:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Er… Can you make it home okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.83,0:08:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you're so kind! A gentleman, even!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.33,0:08:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not a gentleman. I plan \Non going straight home.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.17,0:08:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.83,0:08:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,No way I'd get drunk from that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.67,0:08:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That sounds like something drunk people say.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.21,0:08:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm telling you, I'm really not drunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.58,0:08:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I can't get drunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.38,0:08:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how much alcohol I drink,\Na part of me always stays calm.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.74,0:09:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I can even see what kind of face I'm making.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.63,0:09:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if I laugh and get wild,\NI feel like it's not actually me doing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.00,0:09:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You're probably the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.71,0:09:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm calling it right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.17,0:09:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I think the hard part starts now.\NJust guessing, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.61,0:09:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.88,0:09:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's a whole lot better \Nthan it was before.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.96,0:09:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought she would never change.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.46,0:09:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You're probably the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.26,0:09:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm calling it right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.04,0:09:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't get drunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.21,0:09:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You surprised me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.46,0:09:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, s-sorry…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.95,0:09:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,But you scare too easily!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.38,0:10:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,So?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.67,0:10:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Wanna go to the club?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.71,0:10:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. For now, I mean…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.71,0:10:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, why do you have that blanket?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.91,0:10:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Blanket? Oh you mean the one for my lap?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.84,0:10:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, for your lap, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.17,0:10:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't you have a different one before?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.83,0:10:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You pay more attention \Nto me than I thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.81,0:10:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,N-no… N-not especially \Nor anything, I just…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.83,0:10:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyways, why'd you buy a new blanket\Neven though you already have one?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.50,0:10:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,How many laps do you have? \NAre you a centipede?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.29,0:10:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm not!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.71,0:10:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I bought a magazine and this \Ncame with it! That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.83,0:10:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I do that a lot, because I \Nrealized I have too many blankets
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.19,0:10:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,and don't know what to do with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.46,0:10:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,R-right…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.38,0:10:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe, if our club continues for a little longer,\NI was thinking I'd leave it in the room…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.08,0:10:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,If it continues, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.08,0:10:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It's still locked.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.29,0:11:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess Yukinon hasn't come yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.96,0:11:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go get the key.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.50,0:11:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? U-um, wait…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.25,0:11:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Staff Room
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.08,0:11:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Hikigaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.98,0:11:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.01,0:11:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I came to get the key for our club room.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.16,0:11:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.49,0:11:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, Yukinoshita already came \Nand took the key earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.79,0:11:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I said I'd call her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.50,0:11:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, I don't think you said that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.96,0:11:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That's cause you left before I said it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.42,0:11:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I went ahead and made tea… \NWould you like some?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.46,0:11:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.58,0:11:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Um… About the other day...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.52,0:11:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.83,0:11:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you finish the move okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.13,0:11:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I wouldn't go as far as \Nto call it "moving," though…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.69,0:12:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,And Yuigahama was there to help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.71,0:12:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah, not a problem! It was no big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.13,0:12:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You really helped me out. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.63,0:12:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.00,0:12:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.33,0:12:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I borrowed a DVD, but the student council laptop\Nis too new and doesn't even play DVDs!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.79,0:12:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.46,0:12:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's quite small, but \Nit's a projector, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.88,0:12:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It is!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.88,0:12:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Apparently, it can even display \Nvideos off a smartphone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.82,0:12:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, but it's expensive, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.07,0:12:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, get this!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.50,0:12:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It came entirely out of the student council\Nbudget, which comes at zero personal cost to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.83,0:12:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,That was the worst\Nproduct demo sales presentation ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.25,0:12:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, wait, I'm gonna put the screen up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.99,0:13:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, that was great!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.83,0:13:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So tell me, why were you \Nwatching a movie here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.00,0:13:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? It's not a movie, it's a TV drama.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.69,0:13:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That part doesn't matter…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.29,0:13:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I was watching it for reference.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.75,0:13:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,But if I watched it in the student council room,\NI would seem like I'm slacking off.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.98,0:13:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What does that say about the fact\Nyou chose to watch it here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.82,0:13:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch it at home!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.13,0:13:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I follow the principle of not working\Noutside of designated hours!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.26,0:13:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, what do you mean by "reference?"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.29,0:13:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a graduation \Nceremony this year, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.85,0:13:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,And then something called a \Nthank-you party or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.77,0:14:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The student council has \Nto manage all of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.63,0:14:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, the thank-you party.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.32,0:14:07.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, to be honest, a normal \Nthank-you party is fine,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.99,0:14:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,but when I think about the \None from when I graduated,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.86,0:14:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to make something \Nmore flashy for this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.95,0:14:18.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Um.. And I think the graduates\Nwould be happy with it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.13,0:14:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.04,0:14:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's why you want the prom.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.38,0:14:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! You always just get it \NYukinoshita! You're so great!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.25,0:14:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,A pro…? What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.59,0:14:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,A promenade, otherwise known as a prom.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.95,0:14:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Put simply, it's an abbreviation \Nfor a type of dance.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.17,0:14:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,In high schools overseas,\Nit's the last dance party of the school year.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.00,0:14:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! There was a scene like \Nthat in the drama, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.75,0:14:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, why not just do a normal one?\NWhy do you want to make it a prom?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.08,0:14:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Because, I'm going to be the prom queen!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.21,0:14:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.13,0:14:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That was in the drama, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.33,0:14:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,That scene where they were like
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.19,0:14:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,"let's choose\Nthe hottest boy and girl in our year!" or whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.04,0:15:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,For our grade, the prom king\Nwould undoubtedly be Hayama.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.04,0:15:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's probably true!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.25,0:15:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Basically, Hayama will be the \Nking, and I'll be the qu-
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.13,0:15:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, Hikigaya, this is totally unrelated,\Nbut are you going to get held back a year?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.13,0:15:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,As if.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.79,0:15:20.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.17,0:15:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It'd be the same as spending a year\Nwaiting to retake university entrance exams right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.96,0:15:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,And using your student discount\Nis always a great bargain, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.67,0:15:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't assign that future to me.\NBesides, I'd lose way more than I'd save.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.19,0:15:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, what if you help with \Nthe prom instead, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.00,0:15:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead of? Instead of what?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.88,0:15:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,So, are you seriously going to hold a prom?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.66,0:15:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.58,0:15:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,But it definitely can't happen \Neven if you start it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.92,0:15:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it looks like fun, \Nbut… it also looks difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.30,0:15:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.31,0:15:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Well…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.90,0:15:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.50,0:15:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,But I want to do it… Do you \Nthink that's unacceptable?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.63,0:16:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not a matter of acceptability,\Nbut more that it's not really doable.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.75,0:16:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,There are a multitude of reasons why,\Nbut… I mean, you understand that, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.17,0:16:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.00,0:16:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.15,0:16:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Then the student council will \Ntry to do this on our own.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.79,0:16:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, good decision… Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.25,0:16:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Were you listening?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.54,0:16:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. So we're going to do it on our own.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.34,0:16:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,O-okay. Alright then.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.04,0:16:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,If you change your mind or gain an interest,\Ncome hang out in the student council room!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.29,0:16:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You're always welcome!\NSo much that we won't let you go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.38,0:16:29.55,Default,,0,0,0,,She just wants to run us ragged, doesn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.55,0:16:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I ask you something?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.42,0:16:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.75,0:16:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you want to do so much to hold a prom?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.13,0:16:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.89,0:16:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, because, I mean, I \Nwant to be prom queen…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.50,0:16:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean in two years, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.25,0:16:43.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, well…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.09,0:16:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I've gotta start laying the \Ngroundwork for that now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.58,0:16:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Supposing that a prom is \Nheld two years from now,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.22,0:16:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,you'll be chosen as queen\Neven if you don't lay any groundwork today.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.08,0:16:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,U-um... What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.34,0:16:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm saying there's no real reason\Nyou have to do this right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.89,0:17:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Even next year, there will be no problem…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.12,0:17:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,That won't work!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.29,0:17:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if I suggest holding a prom next year,\Nit probably wouldn't happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.50,0:17:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be forced to give up\Nbecause they'll say we won't have enough time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.54,0:17:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why no matter how difficult \Nit is, and even if it's a flop,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.16,0:17:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to lay the foundations \Nfor my next move!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.51,0:17:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Isshiki…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.68,0:17:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,This has to be done now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.40,0:17:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,If we start now, we may be ready in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.38,0:17:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What and who are you doing this for?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.33,0:17:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,For myself, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.38,0:17:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. Thank you for your answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.92,0:17:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Now then, let's get started.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.83,0:17:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha-? Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.08,0:17:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you for real gonna do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.75,0:17:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my gawd, Yukinoshita! I freakin' love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.59,0:17:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.58,0:18:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,But what was with the third-degree\Nyou just gave me? It was scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.85,0:18:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It'd be great if you'd stop \Ndoing stuff like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.35,0:18:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess we have no choice\Nif that's what the president has decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.54,0:18:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll do our job.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.88,0:18:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep, we will.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.00,0:18:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, can I speak with you two?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.33,0:18:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.42,0:18:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What I just did was on \Nmy own personal volition.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.63,0:18:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no intention of forcing you to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.83,0:18:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,O-okay. What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.33,0:18:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, well… this was not a decision\NI made as club president,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.70,0:18:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,so I don't have the authority \Nto make you help.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.21,0:18:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,But of course, I would be grateful\Nto receive help from you two…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.88,0:18:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Simply, even if it's on my own,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.25,0:18:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I intend to take responsibility for the prom\Nand see it through to completion.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.58,0:18:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Or rather…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.17,0:18:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean we're free to participate or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.50,0:18:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,No, Hikki.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.96,0:18:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yukinon is saying that she wants to try\Nto do this on her own, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.13,0:19:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,This has to be done now…\NIf we start now, we may be ready in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.00,0:19:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe… That applies to me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.25,0:19:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Because...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.92,0:19:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to make a proper start.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.83,0:19:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd be happy if you two would watch over me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.63,0:19:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I won't say a word. But promise me,\Nyou will absolutely not overexert yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.96,0:19:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And if you need manpower \Nthen you have to call us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.38,0:19:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if it's not as the Service Club,\Nyou can call us as your friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.83,0:19:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to help you when that happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.58,0:19:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I promise I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.33,0:19:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.71,0:19:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright! Sounds good to \Nme! How about you, Hikki?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.46,0:19:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Same.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.04,0:19:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I making a mistake?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.59,0:19:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,No, this sounds fine. No idea, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.96,0:19:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You never say anything helpful.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.63,0:19:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I get it, for the most part!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.54,0:19:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay then, thanks for your help, Yukino!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.83,0:19:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What did she just call you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.54,0:20:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm looking forward to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.83,0:20:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Then will you please come\Nto the student council room starting tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.42,0:20:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, I don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.86,0:20:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.00,0:20:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.13,0:20:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Act like you didn't see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.17,0:20:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yukinon.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.46,0:20:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you taking this coat with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.00,0:20:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I don't need it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.25,0:20:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,'Kay!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.64,0:20:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Haruno
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.96,0:20:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be back.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.25,0:20:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.63,0:20:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,We should have some mineral water left.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.96,0:21:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I actually realized it a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.19,0:21:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,There was a place that I couldn't get into,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.53,0:21:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,and though I stand in front of \Nthat door time and time again,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.21,0:21:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I get the feeling that \NI shouldn't disturb it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.75,0:21:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,All I can do is peek in through \Na crack and eavesdrop…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.29,0:21:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, I realized it a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.58,0:22:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew I wanted to go there.\NI wanted nothing more than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.59,0:22:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why, honestly…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.97,0:22:10.97,On Top,,0,0,0,,That Key Was Never Handled\NUntil Today.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.75,0:22:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I never wanted anything genuine.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.88,0:23:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You like chick flick movies \Nlike that, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.79,0:23:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, isn't it a relief \Nthat I prefer chick flicks?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.08,0:23:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Women who say they prefer\NHollywood action blockbusters
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.25,0:23:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,are only saying that to \Nappease their boyfriends.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.88,0:23:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.75,0:23:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,In nine cases out of ten, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.33,0:23:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.20,0:23:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You're breaking the hearts \Nof all the guys out there
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.76,0:23:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,who think their girlfriends \Nactually like the same movies.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.79,0:24:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. But evil women always \Npull moves like that to-
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.75,0:24:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, were you just hitting on me?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.38,0:24:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you say that because you were going \Nto invite me on a movie date after this?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.92,0:24:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry I ruined it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.92,0:24:11.01,On Top,,0,0,0,,Iroha Isshiki is the Strongest Junior,\Nas Expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.01,0:24:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously? There's no point now…

